              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16171349/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chenyingfeng/" class=" " title="ca">ca</a>
                (动态性复杂：环状因果互动及变化)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
